        "localization": {
          "name": "Elemental Eruption",
          "description": "500% damage to 2 enemies, and heals the user for 100% of max HP if damage is dealt. This attack ignores damage reduction effects.\n\nEnemies damaged by this attack will be granted one of the following effects:\n- Sleep for 200TU, even if they have already slept while on the battlefield if they are a Fire or Light unit.\n- Mega Poison for 200TU if they are a Storm or Earth unit.\n- Stun for 200TU if they are a Water or Dark unit.\n\nLocked for 200TU after the user has entered the battlefield, and locks again after each use. After the first use, unlocks each time the user damages an enemy with a different attack. Sleep and Mega Poison will overwrite other status effects on that enemy. Mega Poison deals 20 times the damage of normal Poison and cannot be overwritten by normal Poison or Super Poison. This is not considered a Combo Burst type active skill.",
          "selected": "500% damage, ignores damage reduction & heals"
        }
      }
